## I18n
- Use `I18n.t`/`I18n.l`; keep translations in `config/locales/*.yml`. Avoid inline strings for user-facing copy.

## Time zones
- Set `config.time_zone` to the app default; store in UTC (AR default) and convert for display.
```ruby
# config/application.rb
config.time_zone = "America/New_York" # example
```
